<plot>Nikola Stedul, a former Yugoslavian Freedom Fighter, lives in Fife, Scotland with his family. A plan to assassinate him is concocted and the gun-man Vinco Sindicic is sent to the quiet Scottish town to shoot the outspoken exile. After sitting and watching the house for a week, the assassin shoots Stedul several times as he leaves his house for a walk. The plan fails and Stedul survives. Based on a true story.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?603001</url></doc>
